{"tid":1289794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［理性討論] 其實林鄭呢刻就算落台又有咩用？","createTime":"2019-07-06T08:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-06T15:06:55.000Z","uid":38056,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"995ba696586abf7826ab1d949bd487bd8327e5ed","tid":1289794,"uid":38056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:57:39.000Z","msg":"成日話五大訴求一個都不能少<br />\n但林鄭問責下台<br />\n咪又係推第二個看似傀儡上台<br />\n然後繼續賣港<br />\n林鄭宜家已經係跛腳鴨政府<br />\n至少佢在任嘅時候<br />\n我唔認為佢有能力重推23條<br />\n咁不如擺佢喺到但乜都推唔郁對我地咪仲有利？<br />\n<br />\n取而代之<br />\n我地呢刻應該食住個勢<br />\n爭取真 雙普選<br />\n永遠取消功能組別<br />\n否則只會歷史不斷重演<br />\n連部份建制都打開口牌<br />\n話可以無831前設下重啓政改<br />\n何樂而不為？<br />\n<br />\n其餘4樣一步都不可退！"},{"pid":"7873ae99f6cb915559f421546a114d2fe2114369","tid":1289794,"uid":221696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T08:58:59.000Z","msg":"有無人印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote> <blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykF0iKu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykF0iKu.png&h=e791e1a6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4VWBwa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4VWBwa.png&h=c69769d7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LBEXk4h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLBEXk4h.png&h=add7d72c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AFtk3bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAFtk3bc.png&h=12717881&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZF7Jbd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZF7Jbd.png&h=011957c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yXh5pz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yXh5pz.png&h=517cf7bb&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BtXh5uE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2